{{See|Joke}}
==English==
===Etymology===
from Latin [[iocus]].
===Noun===
'''joke''' (''plural:'' [[jokes]])

#An amusing story or one with an amusing ending.
#A [[pun]].
#Something said or done for amusement to the detriment of someone else.

====Synonyms====
*(2): [[play on words]]
*(3): [[giggle]], [[laugh]]

