===Intransitive verb===
'''to joke''' (''[[present participle]]'' '''joking''', ''[[past tense]] and [[past participle]]'' '''joked''')

#To do or say something for amusement rather than seriously.
#:''I didn’t mean what I said—I was only joking.''

